<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/financial-reporting-council> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Financial Reporting Council (FRC) promotes transparency and integrity in business. It regulates auditors, accountants and actuaries, and sets the UK’s Corporate Governance and Stewardship Codes. FRC is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Business and Trade ."@en .
